    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的家人处于危险之中，而你被卷入了一场致命的游戏来拯救他们。仔细分析每个进入你车内的罪犯，了解他们的特征，并通过正确的策略在不激怒他们的情况下生存下来。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >观察</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>危险乘客</strong>：杀手，小偷，骗子……每个人都有不同的个性和危险级别。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>心理分析：</strong>根据乘客的行为确定罪犯类型，并在不激怒他们的情况下完成旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098050/extras/5658f85fb84a3a64c8ce64935b9dba11.poster.avif?t=1765370073\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098050/extras/5658f85fb84a3a64c8ce64935b9dba11.webm?t=1765370073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098050/extras/5658f85fb84a3a64c8ce64935b9dba11.mp4?t=1765370073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >黑客</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用你电脑上的应用程序来获取你需要的信息，或者通过深网强行获取它。也许你能在深网中找到如何解除放在你车下的炸弹的信息。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098050/extras/44afa1384c7a344d6c882b51d1168134.poster.avif?t=1765370073\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098050/extras/44afa1384c7a344d6c882b51d1168134.webm?t=1765370073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098050/extras/44afa1384c7a344d6c882b51d1168134.mp4?t=1765370073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >生存</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>完成任务：</strong>利用日志中的笔记，在不激怒乘客的情况下将他们送到目的地，如果你活下来，向BK26发送你的笔记。<br><strong>错误的时间，错误的地点：</strong>无论是在车内还是车外，都没有生还的保证。你必须时刻保持警惕。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098050/extras/8b2754054891892d46112a6e50131db2.poster.avif?t=1765370073\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098050/extras/8b2754054891892d46112a6e50131db2.webm?t=1765370073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098050/extras/8b2754054891892d46112a6e50131db2.mp4?t=1765370073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >决定你的命运</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有没有人可以帮你？完成BK26的任务，或者找到其他决定命运的方式。不为自己，而是为你的家人。</p>",
